## Pipeline Flow

```
Signal Scanner (3033)
  ↓ signals
Agent 2 Research (3035)
  ↓ company profile
Agent 3 Scorer (3038)
  ↓ score + forward
Agent 4 Contact Research (3036)
  ↓ confirmed contact
Agent 5 Outreach Drafter (3037)
  ↓ approved draft → Gmail Drafts
Agent 6 Email Scan (3034)
  ↓ inbound replies → Attio
```

