## agent6 module exports — confirmed 09 Mar 2026

Always check exports before writing instruction files:
```bash
grep -n "^export" "Track8 context/track-8/agent6-email-scan/modules/"*.js
```

Confirmed exports:
- gmail.js: `searchMessages(query)`, `readMessage(id)`, `closeClient()`
- classify.js: `classifyReply(subject, body)` — pass strings, NOT email object
- attio.js: `lookupByEmail`, `updateStatus`, `setNextAction`, `appendNote`, `createTask`

NOT exported (internal): `parseSearchResults`, `parseEmailContent`, `isBounce`
